          .col-xs-12
            h1.title Jeffrey&nbsp;Terry
      .col-sm-6.main-description-text.
        Hi, my name's Jeff, and I just used global warming to break the ice! Right now, my interests include entrepreneurship, intelligent robotics, and computer science education. The big projects I'm working on include a company I'm co-founding called XiP Technologies, an intelligent automation system for my apartment, and a computer science education program at a middle school in Norman. When I'm not working on projects or doing classwork, I enjoy reading, playing basketball, and, of course, taking long walks on the beach.
